SummaryProjectCardView is a CardView
    main column
        DisplayProject
            bold
            raise blue alert when (HasProjectComments)
                mouse over text is "CommentsExists"
        Description
        text of "<ProjectDateRange.BeginDate>_-_<ProjectDateRange.EndDate>"
            left align
        BudgetTemplateChangesPendingMF
            display as tag
                color of red
            visible when (HasBudgetChanges)
